<br />
Uptime DPS: 149.90
<br />
Total DPS: 96.66
<br />

<br />
If you consider that the epic pet, rogue, and warrior had nearly the same total uptime, either the warrior and rogue need some serious upgrades or Epic pet truly is bad ass.
<br />

